Pre-Game Insights: Cook Islands coach Tuka Tisam expressed confidence in the team's readiness and preparation for the match against Tonga.
Tonga coach Kilifi Uele emphasized the importance of their planning process and preparation for the World Cup campaign.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was the opening game of the Oceania qualifying series for the 2026 FIFA Men's World Cup.
Only one team from the group would advance to Group B, with further matches scheduled in Fiji and Vanuatu.
